tighten spending and make major changes in its social programs 
instead of revising its tax system 
after fighting tremendous odds after fighting tremendous 
money after fighting tremendous political influence and power 
finally ladies and gentlemen you did it again duke told 
supporters in his metairie district 
jefferson parish assessor lawrence chehardy another opponent 
said voters rejected the package because they did not believe that 
state government has its house in order 
