former dictator hugo banzer has 
demonstrated a lasting broadly based popularity in his campaign to 
win election sunday to the presidency he once took by force 
the 62yearold retired army general is playing to enthusiastic 
audiences from all social levels of this poor largely indian 
nation of 6 million 
his popularity is a curious phenomenon at a time when 
